{
  "text": "Dose rate measurements yielded no problems, and results ranged from 1.23 to 2.65 Gy/ka with values around 1.5 Gy/ka for most samples (see Table 2 ). These values are larger than those reported by [CITATION_1] for Roer Valley Graben sediments, likely due to larger loam contents of the present samples.",
